<paragraph base="F6126963" id="IAS16_81E"><paranum>81E</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IAS 16"/><data name="paranum" value="81E"/></prolog><body><p id="IAS16_P0305"><xref base="F6893271" href="IAS16_5.dita#IAS16_5" id="IAS16_X0278">Paragraph 5</xref> was amended by <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Improvements to IFRSs</ph></ph> issued in May 2008. An entity shall apply that amendment prospectively for annual periods beginning on or after 1 January 2009. Earlier application is permitted if an entity also applies the amendments to <xref base="F16455256" href="../ias40/IAS40_8.dita#IAS40_8" id="IAS16_X0279">paragraphs 8</xref>, <xref base="F16455257" href="../ias40/IAS40_9.dita#IAS40_9" id="IAS16_X0280">9</xref>, <xref base="F16455258" href="../ias40/IAS40_22_DELETED.dita#IAS40_22" id="IAS16_X0281">22</xref>, <xref base="F16455259" href="../ias40/IAS40_48.dita#IAS40_48" id="IAS16_X0282">48</xref>, <xref base="F16455292" href="../ias40/IAS40_53.dita#IAS40_53" id="IAS16_X0283">53</xref>, <xref base="F16455293" href="../ias40/IAS40_53A.dita#IAS40_53A" id="IAS16_X0284">53A</xref>, <xref base="F16455294" href="../ias40/IAS40_53B.dita#IAS40_53B" id="IAS16_X0285">53B</xref>, <xref base="F16455295" href="../ias40/IAS40_54.dita#IAS40_54" id="IAS16_X0286">54</xref>, <xref base="F16455296" href="../ias40/IAS40_57.dita#IAS40_57" id="IAS16_X0287">57</xref> and <xref base="F16455297" href="../ias40/IAS40_85B.dita#IAS40_85B" id="IAS16_X0288">85B</xref> of <xref base="F6893272" href="../ias40/IAS40_TOC0001.dita#IAS40_TOC0001" id="IAS16_X0289">IAS 40</xref> at the same time. If an entity applies the amendment for an earlier period it shall disclose that fact.</p></body></paragraph>